RESOURCE.STRING: Cummins INSITE
Starter Lockout Relay Driver Override Test
This test allows the user to manually override the starter lockout relay driver.
This test is not supported by the current calibration.

Initial Conditions
1. Engine stopped
Steps
1. Select the desired Override position
2. Select Start
3. Monitor operation of the Starter Lockout Relay
Additional Information
1. If Close is selected, ensure that the engine can be started. If Open is selected, ensure that the engine cannot be started
2. Test is used to manually override the starter lockout relay driver
3. Test will run for a maximum of %1!d! seconds
4. If required, select Stop to end the test early
This test is not enabled in ECM
